reviewText:
Wow I hear about these web series from my friends and I decide to buy the DVD.
I have to admit I really loved and I cant recall how many times I watched it already. It's really funny and I like all the episodes.
Well done guys keep it up and I am your Number 1 fan
I highly recommends it.
Hope to see more from this group.  Are there other works I can get from Laquita?  Can't believe I just heard of this from a college buddy.  Looking forward to season 2.
